7. when the voting pod goes down, then another pod comes up

 

8. delete worker pod:
when worker pod is deleted, a new pod came up - logs of all the votes are gone as they are present in that pods, but the actual data is there
delete db pod:
when the db pod is terminating, a new db pod is came up
all the data is deleted - so it is a stateless application

 

10.
the worker restart happens after the db pod goes down as its not able to access the db would have caused a code break or ran into an exception

 

11. the pods restart themselves and result pod comes up
